testcase.name: COVIDcode Study Provider Enrollment Questionnaire Submission Group 1 User
testcase.system-out: Given a COVIDcode Study Provider user has logged in to the COVIDcode Study application.skipped When the COVIDcode Study Provider fills out an Enrollment Questionnaire for a "Group 1" who says "Yes" to join the study.skipped And enters users full name, required information, and demographics information.skipped But does not enter Disease Course and Exposures and Risk Factors information.skipped And Submits the enrollment questionnaire....................................skipped Then the enrollment questionnaire should be successfully submitted..........skipped
